==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Gunroom
<hw>Gun"room`</hw> <pr>(g⟦ucr⟧n"r⟦oomac⟧m`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Naut.)</fld> <def>An apartment on the after end of the lower gun
deck of a ship of war, usually occupied as a messroom by the
commissioned officers, except the captain; -- called
<altname>wardroom</altname> in the United States navy.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gunshot</ent>⟦br⟧
